---
title: Dukkah Spiced Chicken with Herby Lentil Salad and Roasted Veggies
description: We love a good Chicken with Lentil Salad and Carrot and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/dukkah-spiced-chicken-c16f9c27-e028864b.jpg
